00:24:13.350 --> 00:24:15.809
for that accessibility on the Internet as
we were talking about today.

00:24:15.809 --> 00:24:19.080
It's just not been passed yet.
&gt;&gt;Susan Wojcicki: Can you say a little bit

00:24:19.080 --> 00:24:23.159
about what it is, just so everyone here knows.
&gt;&gt;Marlee Matlin: Well, Jack can do that better

00:24:23.159 --> 00:24:27.509
than I can.
&gt;&gt;Jack Jason: It's basically --

00:24:27.509 --> 00:24:31.019
&gt;&gt;Marlee Matlin: Talk --
&gt;&gt;Jack Jason: Yes, as Marlee said, back in

00:24:31.019 --> 00:24:36.759
1990 and then again in 1994, legislation was
passed that required broadcasters to closed

00:24:36.759 --> 00:24:40.879
caption, because they wouldn't do it themselves.
