I mean, I think if I were in your child's
shoes, --

00:31:01.799 --> 00:31:03.489
&gt;&gt;&gt;Yes.
Five years old.

00:31:03.489 --> 00:31:06.809
&gt;&gt;Marlee Matlin: -- five years old.
&gt;&gt;&gt;If you were.

00:31:06.809 --> 00:31:10.159
&gt;&gt;Marlee Matlin: What I would want from my
